Onboarding/Recruiting protocol v1.0_937883

Condensed protocol:
- Read essay, letter, pledge
- Take verbal pledge before God and a Guardian, Make UTXO pledge
- 




How to join the Canadian National Guard:

1. Go to www.CanadianNationalGuard.com

2. Read & understand the essay

3. Read the letter

4. Read the Guardian Pledge

5. Declare a verbal pledge before God and a witness

6. Pledge a UTXO on chain (121,121 sats)

7. Share the essay and letter with everyone you know

8. Study Guardian resources (Bible, Bitcoin, Charter, Health)

9. Train your body

10. Educate your community

11. Attend monthly Guardian council meetings

12. Work for the Canadian National Guard [optional]
